{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/selector-pseudo-element-blacklist/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/selector-pseudo-class-blacklist/","description":"selector-pseudo-class-whitelist 指定允许的伪类选择器的白名单。 此规则忽略使用变量插值的选择器，例如 :#{$variable} {}。 选项 array|string|regex: \\[\"array\", \"of\", \"unprefixed\",…","title":""},"body":"<h1 id=\"selector-pseudo-class-whitelist\"><a href=\"#selector-pseudo-class-whitelist\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>selector-pseudo-class-whitelist</h1>\n<p>指定允许的伪类选择器的白名单。</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">  <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:hover</span> {}\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/** ↑\n * 这个伪类选择器 */</span></code></pre>\n<p>此规则忽略使用变量插值的选择器，例如 <code>:#{$variable} {}</code>。</p>\n<h2 id=\"选项\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>选项</h2>\n<p><code>array|string|regex</code>: <code>[\"array\", \"of\", \"unprefixed\", /pseudo-classes/ or \"/regex/\"]|\"pseudo-class\"|/regex/</code></p>\n<p>如果字符串用 <code>\"/\"</code> 包围（例如 <code>\"/^nth-/\"</code>），则将其解释为正则表达式。这允许方便的简写，例如：<code>/^nth-/</code> 将匹配 <code>nth-child</code>、<code>nth-last-child</code>、<code>nth-of-type</code> 等。</p>\n<p>给定：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-js\">[<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"hover\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"/^nth-/\"</span>]</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:focus</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:first-of-type</span> {}</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:hover</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:nth-of-type(5)</span> {}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:nth-child(2)</span> {}</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/selector-pseudo-class-whitelist.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/selector-pseudo-class-whitelist/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/selector-pseudo-class-whitelist/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/selector-pseudo-class-whitelist/index.html.f3ca4237cebe49977cbae4cde0f2e2b3.json"}